title: Total population of Malaysia 2024
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Inhabitants in millions. In total the number of data points it has is 11.
Overall Inhabitants in millions has increased over the Year.
Inhabitants in millions is slightly increasing from 2014 to 2024.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2014 and 2015.
The highest Inhabitants in millions, of value 34.92 was reached at Year 2024
The lowest Inhabitants in millions, of value 30.71 was reported at Year 2014
